      "title": "Sri Lanka to set up SOE restructuring unit",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lanka will set up a separate agency to re-structure state enterprises which are eating up people\u2019s taxes, President Ranil Wickremesinghe said.",
        "Sri Lanka will oversee around 60 state agencies with statements of intent which will be reviewed, he said.",
        "Sri Lanka has already set in motion steps to restructure Ceylon Petroleum Corporation."
      ],
